  "prompt": "Where can I get affordable pest control services for bed bugs in Hawkesbury?",
  "response": "To find affordable pest control services for bed bugs in Hawkesbury, consider the following steps:\n\n1. **Local Pest Control Companies**: Start by searching for pest control companies in Hawkesbury. Some local businesses may offer competitive pricing and special deals. Examples include:\n   - **Hawkesbury Pest Control**\n   - **Ontario Pest Control Services**\n\n2. **Compare Quotes**: Contact multiple companies to get quotes. Be sure to ask about any ongoing promotions or discounts for first-time customers.\n\n3. **Community Recommendations**: Check local community forums, social media groups, or ask neighbors for recommendations. They might know of affordable and reliable services.\n\n4. **DIY Options**: For a more budget-friendly approach, consider DIY methods. Stores like Home Depot or Canadian Tire sell bed bug treatments. However, professional services are usually more effective and thorough.\n\n5. **Government and Non-Profit Programs**: Some areas offer subsidized pest control services through government or non-profit organizations. Check if there are any programs available in Hawkesbury.\n\n6. **Online Reviews**: Websites like Yelp, Google Reviews, and HomeStars can provide insights into the affordability and effectiveness of different pest control services.\n\nBy following these steps, you should be able to find a cost-effective solution for bed bug control in Hawkesbury.",
